4 thanks	not a problem

2 i will traveling to seattle so i need information for there please	any day in particular you need the forecast for or do you just want the whole week for seattle ?
3 for the whole week , please !	the weather next 7 days for seattle is going to be a series of ups and downs from clear_skies on monday to a foggy on wednesday and to frost on friday the highs are forecast to be near 100f with lows near 20f
